<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧和悟净被绑在妖怪们的洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒也被绑着，浮在盐水桶里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三个妖怪在另一个房间里说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那头猪腌好了，一定非常好吃。”象怪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也这么认为。”狮怪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36214</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38810</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，主菜是唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>长生不老一定很好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>象怪点了点头。“把唐僧放上大蒜和调料油炸了吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我去厨房看看有什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等。”大鹏怪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得计划一下。悟空肯定会来救他们的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对。”狮怪说。他摸了摸碎掉的牙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不希望再发生那种事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>象怪看了看自己淤青的鼻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也不希望。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。这次我有个计划。”大鹏怪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们造谣，告诉附近的所有妖怪，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们已经吃了唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空知道后，就会放弃希望，离开这里的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太棒了！”狮怪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>象怪笑了。“这个计划很完美。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空坐在路边，正在想该怎么办。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那些妖怪一直在骗我。”悟空自言自语道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，再也不能等了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116757</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要去那个洞里，救出唐僧他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪们如果攻击我，我就用金箍棒打他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>即使他们哭着求我，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我也绝对不会再相信他们的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看见两个小妖沿路走来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们是谁？”悟空想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他藏在岩石后面，等着妖怪们经过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那些妖怪们运气真好。”一个小妖说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊。”另一个小妖说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155973</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们吃了唐僧，现在可以长生不老了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第一个小妖说。他叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可以长生不老可真好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊。”另一个小妖说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个小妖继续走着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空的心很痛。他伤心极了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的眼里涌出了泪水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我让你失望了，师父！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我没能保护好你，现在你永远也去不了西天了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空双手捂着脸，哭了很久。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，他站了起来，擦了眼泪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道该做什么了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跳到空中，朝西边飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他到了雷音寺。门将让他进去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空走到佛祖面前，弯腰行礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请原谅我，佛祖。我失败了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天，就在刚才，唐僧他……他……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空又大哭起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241556</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佛祖笑了。“别哭，悟空，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241556</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧没事。妖怪们没吃他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空抬头看着佛祖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的吗？”他带着希望问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”佛祖说，“我能看到天上人间的一切。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我知道那些妖怪到底是谁，他们做了什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们骗了你，让你以为他们吃了唐僧，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是想让你放弃希望。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”悟空气得大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些坏妖怪！又骗了我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空用金箍棒打向洞口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291774</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哗啦！洞口被打碎了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三个妖怪跑到外面来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狮怪喊道：“你怎么敢…...”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他抬头一看，大吃一惊。“佛祖！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狮怪和象怪吓得浑身发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一道光闪过，佛祖把两个妖怪变成了普通的动物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有大鹏怪没有害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320016</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他眼里冒着怒火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他朝佛祖飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，佛祖伸出一根手指，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的身体就在空中一动都不能动了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佛祖看向悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你现在可以去救唐僧他们了。我们西天见。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>344351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空弯腰行礼。“谢谢，佛祖。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>